						<div class="fancy-title title-bottom-border">
							<h3>Corporate Values</h3>
						</div>
					<p>
						As Oman Green Building Council (OGBC)is strongly focusing on reducing CO2 emissions and carbon reduction plans, Solar Safety Film Trading represent the SolarGard Saint-Gobain environment protection plan in India by promoting the concept of the energy saving solutions by incorporating with world famous SOLARGARD SAINT-GOBAIN, who is one of the strongest participant of environmental safety activities.
					</p>
					<p>
						SolarGard Saint-Gobain has always been the industry leader with environmental responsibility as a core mission, Solar Gard has earned the esteemed title of Climate Action Leader. SolarGard is committed to manufacture the premium quality products in the most environmentally responsible manner with minimum impact to the environment. SolarGard discover and create new ways to protect, save and renew through lean manufacturing and innovative technology.
					</p>
					<p>
						After years of solid environmental stewardship, SolarGard journey towards environmental excellence began in 2007. Year by year, Solar Gard have shouldered added responsibilities to deliver the solutions against threatening environmental factors to the world . SolarGard’s Environmental Management System is ISO-14011 Certified, and ensures the manufacturing practices control the minimal impact on the environment. SolarGard constantly monitor and improve the energy efficiency, resource conservation, waste management and chemical controls, under ISO 14001-certified management processes.
					</p>
					<p>
						SolarGard has been an active member of Clinton Foundation which stands for better and healthy environment by reducing the energy consumption which may affect our environment tomorrow. SolarGard products have been labeled as Energy Star product which helps to reduce greenhouse gas emissions and other pollutants caused by the inefficient use of energy.
					</p>







